creator: David Nuno
descriptionHtml:
A quick and easy application for compiling your weekly list of groceries. Share your list with friends or family when needed! Designed for a simple list of needs.

Features:

- One simple list
- Simple way to add your groceries
- Share your list via SMS, E-mail and other messaging applications
- Browse your groceries via Wear OS now!
- Home screen widget for an easier and convenient way to check your shopping list
descriptionShort: A very basic app to create your list of groceries.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Fixed UI bug when editing grocery items.
